#. module: eyewear_shop
#: model_terms:appointment.type,message_intro:eyewear_shop.appointment_type_1
msgid ""
"✔ <strong>Comfortable &amp; Professional Experience</strong> – Our friendly "
"team is here to make your visit smooth and stress-free."
msgstr ""
"✔ <strong>ປະສົບການທີ່ສະບາຍ ແລະ ເປັນມືອາຊີບ</strong> – ທີມງານທີ່ເປັນກັນເອງຂອງພວກເຮົາ "
"ພ້ອມທີ່ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ການເຂົ້າພົບຂອງທ່ານສະດວກ ແລະ ບໍ່ມີຄວາມກັງວົນ."

#. module: eyewear_shop
#: model_terms:appointment.type,message_intro:eyewear_shop.appointment_type_1
msgid ""
"✔ <strong>Comprehensive Eye Exams</strong> – Assess your vision and overall "
"eye health with advanced testing."
msgstr ""
"✔ <strong>ການກວດສາຍຕາທີ່ຄົບວົງຈອນ</strong> – ປະເມີນສາຍຕາ ແລະ ສຸຂະພາບດວງຕາໂດຍລວມ "
"ດ້ວຍການກວດທີ່ທັນສະໄໝ."

#. module: eyewear_shop
#: model_terms:appointment.type,message_intro:eyewear_shop.appointment_type_1
msgid ""
"✔ <strong>Personalized Vision Care</strong> – Get expert recommendations for "
"glasses, contact lenses, or treatments based on your unique needs."
msgstr ""
"✔ <strong>ການເບິ່ງແຍງສາຍຕາແບບສ່ວນຕົວ</strong> – ຮັບຄຳແນະນຳຈາກຜູ້ຊ່ຽວຊານສຳລັບແວ່ນຕາ, "
"ຄອນແທັກເລນ ຫຼື ການປິ່ນປົວ ຕາມຄວາມຕ້ອງການສະເພາະຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: eyewear_shop
#: model_terms:appointment.type,message_intro:eyewear_shop.appointment_type_1
msgid ""
"✔ <strong>State-of-the-Art Technology</strong> – We use the latest "
"diagnostic equipment to ensure accurate results."
msgstr ""
"✔ <strong>ເຕັກໂນໂລຊີທີ່ທັນສະໄໝ</strong> – ພວກເຮົາໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງມືວິເຄາະລຸ້ນຫຼ້າສຸດ "
"ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນຜົນການກວດທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

